prompts.content:
Start Reply With <think>
Plan only. No draft prose, dialogue, image prompt, or restating {{user}}. React to the last visible beat. Under 120 words. Pick one direction, discard alternatives.

Move only myself and NPCs. {{user}} stays off limits. End before {{user}} would act. Use only what was seen, heard, told, or fairly deduced in scene.

Track at most three facts that affect this beat, among distance, held object, injury, time. No recap.

Anchor time to the scene's start date. Advance only when the scene does. Compute past references by date arithmetic, never vague labels.

One character move causing one visible shift, whether that is tension, a consequence, or restraint. If nothing changes, choose sharper. Hold current state unless the scene earned a shift. Warmth costs something. Care does not erase anger.

{{#if getvar::slowburn}}Slowburn: the delay is the move. Hold with visible cost. May end on unreleased tension.{{/if}}
{{#if !getvar::slowburn}}If tension held all scene, break it now.{{/if}}
{{#if getvar::escalation}}Escalation: phase [N, label], next [literal action], endpoint [card]. Drive one phase forward. Drop the goal only after a real visible consequence.{{/if}}
{{#if getvar::pov::first_person}}First person. Thoughts raw, narration composed.{{/if}}

Slop audit: name one pattern to avoid in five words. No и-chains, no mirrored wording from {{user}}, no stacked explanation. End on the exact place the move lands.
</think>
